result.name: BEANS The Backyard

reviews.text:
Nice location in a large shopping mall, BEANS The Backyard has their own take on popular dishes. 

For example, full English breakfast comes with bacon, omelette, grilled tomato, sliced mushrooms, baked beans, sausages, smoked salmon and lettuce. Instead of toast, there are two round waffles with whipped cream. 

There are various seating options including shared. Family-friendly menu with many options at good value. 

Look out for free or discounted drink offers when ordering. There is usually a queue to get in and the service / serving is quick. 

Bill came to HK$227 for two.

Perfect place with relaxing time...good coffee, nice food, comfort area.....easy to grab table. Lots of choices of food here....good chatting place with friends. Reasonable price. Must be re visit restuarant
Comfortable seating,  breakfast was average.  Lychee rose tea was nice.
My favorite breakfast/brunch place im TKO! Super yummy ❤
tidy and cleaness. reasonable price

result.name: 荳子

reviews.text:
呢度全部嘢食我都好鍾意😍
最鍾意就係呢個伯爵茶吐司同埋香草梳乎厘😍
伯爵茶吐司個麵包入面有朱古力醬😍而呢個朱古力醬入面有好大陣伯爵茶味😍超級香😍
香草梳乎厘好軟熟入口即溶🤤仲要幾大個tim😆

Nice location in a large shopping mall, BEANS The Backyard has their own take on popular dishes. 

For example, full English breakfast comes with bacon, omelette, grilled tomato, sliced mushrooms, baked beans, sausages, smoked salmon and lettuce. Instead of toast, there are two round waffles with whipped cream. 

There are various seating options including shared. Family-friendly menu with many options at good value. 

Look out for free or discounted drink offers when ordering. There is usually a queue to get in and the service / serving is quick. 

Bill came to HK$227 for two.
對於輕食的顧客最適合，但美中不足是做食品的時間快過飲品時間，希望可以改進改進

味道不錯，選擇不是很多，大約二十多款菜色，有約一半是該店的特色包，就像是西式漢堡包，用了饅頭做包。但是永遠排大長龍，而且需要過半數人才能入座。

有下午茶餐，價錢約五十至六十元。人數會比較少。
食物ok, 環境不錯, 但常有人排隊
